Alias       Bd_SIGNAL     B0
Alias       Bdbar_SIGNAL  anti-B0
ChargeConj  Bd_SIGNAL     Bdbar_SIGNAL

Alias   MyKs    K_S0
ChargeConj MyKs MyKs

Decay Bd_SIGNAL
  1.000        MyKs     nu_e    anti-nu_e                PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Bdbar_SIGNAL

Decay MyKs
  1.000        pi+        pi-                    PHSP;
Enddecay

End
